title: Start the Schwifty NFT consumer chain
description: You feel schwifty already? You have passed the test of the first proposal. Let's get real! This is the proposal to create the consumer chain "schwifty-1", the first ICS consumer chain with an NFT module. Visit https://github.com/clydecarver/ics-testnets/tree/main/game-of-chains-2022/schwifty for details on this proposal's data and how to join the chain.
